Class OutbackRanchFarm

java.lang.Object
main.Farm
main.OutbackRanchFarm
public class OutbackRanchFarm
extends Farm
Extends the Farm class to an OutbackRanchFarm, which has its own set of food items, crop items, crops and animals with custom attributes.
Version:
1.0, May 2020.
Author:
